source: TEXT_CMNDEFRELICWEAPON025CANCELNOTE_00168_GJUSANA_000_000<tab>...Hm? I can't very well dispose of something you don't have, now, can I?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRELICWEAPON025CANCELNOTE_00168_GJUSANA_000_000<tab>Na, du bist mir aber ein komischer Vogel. Du hast doch gar keine Ephemeridentafel.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRELICWEAPON025CANCELNOTE_00168_GJUSANA_000_100<tab>...Really? Well, I suppose the moldy old book <var 1A 02 /var>was<var 1A 01 /var> bound for the furnace any─errr...I mean, it breaks my heart to see a piece of history treated like so many pages of soiled parchment, but who am I to argue with a customer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRELICWEAPON025CANCELNOTE_00168_GJUSANA_000_100<tab>Du brauchst die Ephemeridentafel nicht mehr? Na, mir soll's recht sein. Ich hätte die Dinger sowieso über kurz oder lang entsorgt.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRELICWEAPON025CANCELNOTE_00168_00010<tab>All progress within <var 31 ((EventItem)) 03E8020202 /var> will be lost. Are you certain you wish to proceed?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRELICWEAPON025CANCELNOTE_00168_00010<tab>Wenn du <var 32 ((EventItem)) 04E802020502 /var> wegwirfst, geht dein darauf verzeichneter Fortschritt verloren. Willst du das wirklich tun?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRELICWEAPON025CANCELNOTE_00168_GJUSANA_000_050<tab>There. It's done. That particular bit of history will never bother you again. I hope you're happy now.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRELICWEAPON025CANCELNOTE_00168_GJUSANA_000_050<tab>In Ordnung, das wäre erledigt. Wenn du wieder eine Tafel erwerben möchtest, sprich mich einfach an.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRELICWEAPON025CANCELNOTE_00168_SYSTEM_000_055<tab>You throw away a book from the Trials of the Braves.
